cs.CL, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.NE, cs.SD 

This paper deals with natural language processing tasks, specifically multi-sentence tasks, using deep pretrained transformers. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.CL (Computation and Language). The paper also discusses the use of machine learning techniques, which suggests the sub-categories cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.LG (Learning). The paper also mentions the computation time, which suggests the sub-category cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing). Finally, the paper discusses pretraining on a large dataset, which suggests the sub-category cs.SD (Sound).
